# gromox-queue

A simple local check for CheckMK to notify about stuck messages in `/var/lib/gromox/queue/save`.

## Installation
Place/link script into `/usr/lib/check_mk_agent/local` and make it executable.
To limit it's execution to e.g. every 15 minutes place it in the subfolder "900" (seconds).

## Configuration
A default configuration will be automatically created in `/etc/checkmk/gromox-queue.cfg` where you can set a service name and thresholds.
